
---

**StreamPathTracker**  
**Description:**  
Plots live metrics in a continuously updating stream with directional flow and variable trail persistence.

```markdown
# StreamPathTracker - Live Metric Flow Plotter

StreamPathTracker renders real-time values as a smooth flowing line with emphasis on velocity and trend direction.

## Features
- Adjustable refresh rate  
- Fade-out trail effect  
- Built using Matplotlib

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/StreamPathTracker.git
cd StreamPathTracker
python visualize.py
